query:
SELECT s.id, s.name, s.email, s.personalId, s.status, p.id as personal_id, p.businessName 
FROM students s 
LEFT JOIN personals p ON s.personalId = p.id 
WHERE s.email = 'brunogiordany@gmail.com';
